The confessions that are posted are those that are submitted; not the opinions of the blog owners. All the confessions will be anonymous when posted. Feel free to submit photos along with your confession if you would like as well.

summary: Listen Now To David Tennant Does A Podcast With... Krysten Ritter  A new episode of David Tennant’s podcast series David Tennant...
caption:
Listen Now To David Tennant Does A Podcast With… Krysten Ritter 

A new episode of David Tennant’s podcast series David Tennant Does A Podcast With… is now live. This week David’s guest is American actress, model, author, musician and director Krysten Ritter.

Krysten is a well known star of the screen with roles as lead superhero Jessica Jones on the Marvel series Jessica Jones and the crossover miniseries The Defenders, Jane Margolis on the AMC drama series Breaking Bad, and Chloe on the ABC comedy series Don’t Trust the B— in Apartment 23.

Listen to the podcast now on Spotify, iTunes, Acast or wherever you get your podcasts from!
